### 38.12 Error Handling

If validation cannot be completed due to system unavailability:

| Scenario | Action |
|----------|--------|
| T24 Unavailable | Queue action, retry in 15 minutes |
| CRP Unavailable | Use last known risk status with flag |
| Multiple Failures | Escalate to IT Support |
| Timeout (>30 sec) | Log error, continue with warning |

**Failsafe Principle:** If validation cannot be confirmed, the system must NOT proceed with consequence management actions.

